  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795511\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tIt was another <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/turbulent\" target=\"_blank\">turbulent</a> day on China's share market today. Share prices fell sharply, underlining continued fears about the financial <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stability\" target=\"_blank\">stability</a> of the Chinese economy. Those fears are being felt as far away as Brazil. Once upon a time, Brazil was a member of the much feted BRIC group of promising, emerging market economies. This year, the IMF thinks the Brazilian economy will shrink by one and a half percent. That's in part because as China's economic growth slows, it's buying less of Brazil's big exports - commodities such as soybeans and natural resources such as <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/copper\" target=\"_blank\">copper</a>. Meantime Brazil's government is trying to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/salvage\" target=\"_blank\">salvage</a> its economy by balancing its books and cutting back on spending. And as our South America correspondent Daniel Gallas reports from Sao Paulo, everyone's feeling the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/pinch\" target=\"_blank\">pinch</a>.</p>\n<p>\n\tI'm standing outside a job centre inside a train station in Sao Paulo's Bras neighbourhood. This is one of the places where workers who have lost their jobs in the past few weeks come to to collect unemployment benefits. But rules have changed and it is now harder to claim them.</p>\n<p>\n\tThe changes make life more difficult. Unemployment benefit is something you can count on when in need, but now we've lost that right in some cases. That's bad for workers.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795511/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795511\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798512/\">世界身高报告：荷兰人最高 你猜中国人排第几</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797664/\">2万封邮件爆希拉里选举黑幕 川普表示我笑了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798242/\">囧研究：多少钱够你维持一段友谊？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797394/\">套路还是老的好：人家再也不要网络相亲了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797635/\">视频：老美来教你！地道美语发音要这么练</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797254/\">2016世界先生冠军是他 这脸这身材我的鼻血啊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796263/\">拉丁美食手绘地图：当吃货同时是个牛逼画手</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798521/\">5部提高英式英语的最佳电影</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797621/\">女游客野生动物园下车被老虎咬这事 你怎么看</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797203/\">脱欧后英国经济急剧下降 这么作你们悔了吗？</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a