  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201410/f60ca38bfb2b48e299d6d71fa1de3cb1.jpg\" style=\"height: 287px; width: 460px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英乐天天唱》是一档模仿唱歌类节目，目的在于提升大家的英语口语能力。主持人会在每期节目中选取好听的歌曲片段，并给出发音提示和模仿示例。喜欢听音乐的童鞋可要积极参与哦！<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135241930/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201504/538b1acc-fdd2-4d52-a0bd-920ed3309a72.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t肖恩&middot;沃德（Shayne Ward）是英国歌唱选秀节目&ldquo;The X Factor&rdquo;2005年度总冠军，一颗在英国乐坛冉冉升起的新星，Shayne Ward正在用自己俊朗的外表和优美高亢的声线征服全世界的乐迷。在赢得歌唱比赛之后，Shayne发行了2张个人单曲《That&rsquo;s My Goal》和《No Promises》。随着前两支个人单曲的成功，Shayne Ward推出了个人的首张同名专辑《肖恩&middot;沃德》。Shayne Ward在音乐事业上已经取得多项了不起的成就，Shayne Ward旋风正在席卷整个英国。这一切的一切都显示他具有成为一个乐坛巨星的潜质，预示着他美好的未来。</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795366\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t讲解：<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795366\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t模唱部分：<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795366\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tBaby life was good to me.<br />\n\tBut you just made it better<br />\n\tI love the way you stand by me<br />\n\tthrought any kind of weather</p>\n<p>\n\tI don't wanna run away.<br />\n\tJust wanna make your day<br />\n\tWhen you feel the world is on your shoulders</p>\n<p>\n\tDon't wanna make it worse.<br />\n\tJust wanna make us work<br />\n\tBaby tell me I will do whatever</p>\n<p>\n\tIt feels like nobody ever know me until you knew me<br />\n\tFeels like nobody ever love me until you loved me<br />\n\tFeels like nobody ever touch me until you touched me<br />\n\tBaby nobody, nobody,until you</p>\n<p>\n\tBaby it just took one hit of you now I'm addicted<br />\n\tYou never know what's missing Till you get everything you need,yeah<br />\n\tI don't wanna run away. Just wanna make your day<br />\n\tWhen you feel the world is on your shoulders<br />\n\tDon't wanna make it worse.Just wanna make us work<br />\n\tBaby tell me I will do whatever</p>\n<p>\n\tSee it was enough to know If I ever let you go.I would be no one<br />\n\tcause I never thought I'd feel All the things you made me feel<br />\n\tWasn't looking for someone until you</p>\n<p>\n\t模唱：<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795366\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135241930/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795366/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795366\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798512/\">世界身高报告：荷兰人最高 你猜中国人排第几</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797664/\">2万封邮件爆希拉里选举黑幕 川普表示我笑了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798242/\">囧研究：多少钱够你维持一段友谊？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797394/\">套路还是老的好：人家再也不要网络相亲了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797635/\">视频：老美来教你！地道美语发音要这么练</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797254/\">2016世界先生冠军是他 这脸这身材我的鼻血啊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796263/\">拉丁美食手绘地图：当吃货同时是个牛逼画手</a></li><li style=\"